Business Brief -- Lomas Financial Corp.:
   Holding in LN Housing
   To Be Sold for $3.3 Million
In addition, LN's board approved the transfer of its
management agreement to an affiliate of EastGroup and Walker
from a Lomas affiliate. That transfer is subject to approval
of LN's shareholders at their annual meeting in April.
Further, LN's board elected two Walker representatives to
its board, increasing the board size to 11 members.
   LN makes mortgage loans on multi-family and commercial
projects.